cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL, cs.MS 

This paper involves the use of deep learning models for image analysis and classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.DL) further supports these sub-categories. Finally, the use of statistical analysis (cs.MS) to evaluate the performance of the models also suggests this sub-category as a possibility.
